name: Love Hurt
description:
Horror Fact #03 

Depression distorts your focus and impacts on your memory. Can be hard when it's happened to yourself. Especially when no one understand or either you keep pulling yourself from the help. Your body can do weird things while depressed. Depression and anxiety come from the things that you love. Either afraid that the things we love is not gonna work, and we'll lose it or we will not gonna get those things we love. Love hurt, be brave on loving things.
